na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"937881dde250ec2f171c565b6584e0c54f0cf6cb","tid":1643531,"uid":165913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQfhE20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQfhE20.jpg&h=97269c44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e66e5c081dabca2316e6b5b38249ff4f49045d78","tid":1643531,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:11:02.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}